<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ReadWriteMutex.ObtainReadLock" Title="ObtainReadLock method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ReadWriteMutex">ReadWriteMutex</PageRef> ->
    ObtainReadLock
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ObtainReadLock</TypeRef> method obtains a read lock for this mutex. This method blocks the calling thread until the lock can be obtained.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[std::unique_ptr<ReadLock> ObtainReadLock();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="std::unique_ptr&lt;ReadLock&gt;">
        A read lock object that holds the lock until it is unlocked or destroyed.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
